{"tid":1096202,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Maths vs Physics","createTime":"2019-04-07T14:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T03:14:16.000Z","uid":242626,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3a94bbd26bc1a9ed12d8d0ad1905c3353acee2","tid":1096202,"uid":242626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m6rfpQXzXu0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm6rfpQXzXu0&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=188da09a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m6rfpQXzXu0</a><br />\n<br />\n以前淨係覺得數學家好似工匠咁，不停努力去研發新工具，之後等物理學家/其他領域嘅人覺得有用就去拎黎用。<br />\n<br />\n不過而家modern physics發展到drive返數學家去探討某一啲新嘅範疇，嗰感覺好正。<br />\n<br />\n條片又好似無乜詳細講有咩例子，有無讀數/物理巴打分享下maths同physics之間嘅互動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},{"pid":"288a381306cbbabe47b1f1f69179ccfa35432e78","tid":1096202,"uid":242626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"都係，物理最終極都要透過實驗去證明，所以數同統計某程度係必需<br />\n<br />\n聽過個老師講<br />\n如果俾個物理學家去研究隻牛，佢會先假設牛係球體，因為有對稱又易計，之後先一步一步加/喊啲嘢去計<br />\n<br />\n但如果換轉係數學家，佢會先去證明牛嘅存在，個著眼點係好唔同"},{"pid":"cac757a97c9ebf963b9a1ffa20b087566c27a0cf","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會考巴今次十卜你唔落"},{"pid":"dbdbf07a7ac3729ca3c50bf328791762fb6535a9","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"288a381306cbbabe47b1f1f69179ccfa35432e78","tid":1096202,"uid":242626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"都係，物理最終極都要透過實驗去證明，所以數同統計某程度係必需<br />\n<br />\n聽過個老師講<br />\n如果俾個物理學家去研究隻牛，佢會先假設牛係球體，因為有對稱又易計，之後先一步一步加/喊啲嘢去計<br />\n<br />\n但如果換轉係數學家，佢會先去證明牛嘅存在，個著眼點係好唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解你會覺得實驗係要數同統計去證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc43938080630499a27de3682d4ed02f61e1cf3f","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cac757a97c9ebf963b9a1ffa20b087566c27a0cf","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會考巴今次十卜你唔落"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"都預咗會有負皮<br />\n討論區都係講自己睇法㗎啦，唔support唔緊要，都可以傾下<br />\n<br />\n數學有好多嘢係唔理應用層面而推出，由定義開始，用邏輯擴展開去，足以證明數學嘅獨立性<br />\n例子係未有密碼學前嘅number theory<br />\n<br />\nPhysics嗰邊，喺我認識範圍入面嘅都會連到一堆數學同統計"},{"pid":"50c71e10f7c852b3b716e3d2e273d819fd0a8cf6","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bc43938080630499a27de3682d4ed02f61e1cf3f","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cac757a97c9ebf963b9a1ffa20b087566c27a0cf","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會考巴今次十卜你唔落"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"都預咗會有負皮<br />\n討論區都係講自己睇法㗎啦，唔support唔緊要，都可以傾下<br />\n<br />\n數學有好多嘢係唔理應用層面而推出，由定義開始，用邏輯擴展開去，足以證明數學嘅獨立性<br />\n例子係未有密碼學前嘅number theory<br />\n<br />\nPhysics嗰邊，喺我認識範圍入面嘅都會連到一堆數學同統計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"物理無咗數學會冇咁完整姐<br />\n唔會無說服力既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係observe到個現象然後用model解釋番個現象,數學係用係個model到,但係observe到個現象可以完全唔關數學事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁個現象真係發生過,唔會因為我用唔到數學解釋就冇說服力<br />\n例子:<br />\n蘋果跌落黎證明萬有引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算無數學既式去形容萬有引力都好,萬有引力始終存在"},{"pid":"ee058c1060dd0830763675589a1595d45a432c9e","tid":1096202,"uid":242626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dbdbf07a7ac3729ca3c50bf328791762fb6535a9","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"288a381306cbbabe47b1f1f69179ccfa35432e78","tid":1096202,"uid":242626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"都係，物理最終極都要透過實驗去證明，所以數同統計某程度係必需<br />\n<br />\n聽過個老師講<br />\n如果俾個物理學家去研究隻牛，佢會先假設牛係球體，因為有對稱又易計，之後先一步一步加/喊啲嘢去計<br />\n<br />\n但如果換轉係數學家，佢會先去證明牛嘅存在，個著眼點係好唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解你會覺得實驗係要數同統計去證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁你由實驗結果去到歸納，詮釋，總結嗰啲都有用都數架嘛<br />\n<br />\n大部分嘅研究係靠班理論佬吹啲model出黎，再用實驗去證明match到個model/equation<br />\n<br />\n而你點判斷喺咁大量嘅sample同error當中，個結果match唔match咪又係用到統計"},{"pid":"a64442fad1166d407806fbddc66f50a5ec67429d","tid":1096202,"uid":14566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"爭咩呀爭 溝埋黎做瀨尿牛丸呀笨"},{"pid":"416dbf7d35a72577e88b815b4c9c2f61b3761e2d","tid":1096202,"uid":132660,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=obCjODeoLVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DobCjODeoLVw&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=9ed6e675\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=obCjODeoLVw</a><br />\nOne helps each other.<br />\n無咗數學，個physical fact/principle依然喺度，只不過你無語言去表達出黎同埋量化咁推導。<br />\n數學係可以好獨立咁發展，推導出啲好靚嘅嘢，但可以好離地咁吹到天花龍鳳而完全無用武之地。<br />\n無微積分就無mechanics/thermodynamics就無heat engine就無工業革命and所有現代生活<br />\n無人幫Einstein 整合佢嘅idea同Riemannian geom嘅話根本無人會理解到GR講緊啲咩<br />\n但你無喺application上嘅需求嘅話亦只會有少數人屎忽痕去深入研究Maths topic，個發展唔會咁快。<br />\n<br />\n利申只識運算唔識數學嘅Phys UG"},{"pid":"e2eb6c979b36803cfa6057570f15b07f9a47b9de","tid":1096202,"uid":60539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:43:02.000Z","msg":"Queen and king<br />\n無必要去掙<br />\n各施其職<br />\n拎兩樣唔同既野去比較有啲無謂"},{"pid":"a057b8842caab8fe2b6da0a165587063ae780c02","tid":1096202,"uid":246023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:47:18.000Z","msg":"數學同物理講到底其實係親兄弟<br />\n大家一家人齊齊整整咪好<br />\n點解成日要搞到你死我活咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9137474017013f53537aae452e98ac2cf4fd25","tid":1096202,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:50:34.000Z","msg":"Feynman個path integral搞到數學家頭痛左幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116f89a397c2c6523a0d99caa9f6f5f2cfa03c8f","tid":1096202,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a057b8842caab8fe2b6da0a165587063ae780c02","tid":1096202,"uid":246023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:47:18.000Z","msg":"數學同物理講到底其實係親兄弟<br />\n大家一家人齊齊整整咪好<br />\n點解成日要搞到你死我活咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:21:37.000Z","msg":"數學同物理似唔同種族的人類多啲"},{"pid":"fbb7d72af4a2be035a95a5efd1dd667d994dc566","tid":1096202,"uid":242626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"116f89a397c2c6523a0d99caa9f6f5f2cfa03c8f","tid":1096202,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a057b8842caab8fe2b6da0a165587063ae780c02","tid":1096202,"uid":246023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:47:18.000Z","msg":"數學同物理講到底其實係親兄弟<br />\n大家一家人齊齊整整咪好<br />\n點解成日要搞到你死我活咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:21:37.000Z","msg":"數學同物理似唔同種族的人類多啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得似一間公司兩個部門<br />\n好多嘢著眼點唔同，但有時又會互相倚賴"},{"pid":"a5d4e9823f3c4be68ceec5faa95896c161e04371","tid":1096202,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"Gauge theory應該算係最經典嘅例子<br />\n(我覺得)"},{"pid":"61e50533d1f16e66b67d2a3252b914b0d6f4d87c","tid":1096202,"uid":78298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603b9e432f5d1583ef3874475a47fd5fb3515d7f","tid":1096202,"uid":26389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"數學同物理點會係兄弟 就算數學內部已經係隔行如隔山<br />\n數學家為數學而數學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4e3b850b45a0789f2f1807bf05f20537a9d985","tid":1096202,"uid":31511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"最撚正係數有好多好超前既結論， 但一直唔知計完個結論係代表乜， 直到後期有物理範疇用得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad654e1ddfb962b10dc57142382b1477ddef6c93","tid":1096202,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61e50533d1f16e66b67d2a3252b914b0d6f4d87c","tid":1096202,"uid":78298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"但physics最重要就係計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d35a9590ec5956e280baf038d6d079a311ae358","tid":1096202,"uid":126831,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"Quantum physic 要好多abstract algebra, Lie algebra ，Group theory.<br />\nHeat, electromagnetism  又要用到vector calculus, ODE/PDE，再深入少少就optimization去control system 或者 用ODE system 去discribe。電腦系統就用discrete maths。<br />\n<br />\n總結而言，物理其實係用到好多maths, 數學係一種更pure 方法來表示物理.  數學好多時係用來支持物理。你讀數可以完全唔識物理，但你讀物理就一定要識好多數學。<br />\n<br />\n數學同物理個爭論，就好似美斯C朗爭論邊個係球王，其實冇意思。"},{"pid":"339e4e358ed2fc49848ce0a4aeebdc1f86b81b05","tid":1096202,"uid":78298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad654e1ddfb962b10dc57142382b1477ddef6c93","tid":1096202,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61e50533d1f16e66b67d2a3252b914b0d6f4d87c","tid":1096202,"uid":78298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"但physics最重要就係計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd30650acfd8f3cb5120bf50056b4e3a1fd1852","tid":1096202,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"50c71e10f7c852b3b716e3d2e273d819fd0a8cf6","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bc43938080630499a27de3682d4ed02f61e1cf3f","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cac757a97c9ebf963b9a1ffa20b087566c27a0cf","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會考巴今次十卜你唔落"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"都預咗會有負皮<br />\n討論區都係講自己睇法㗎啦，唔support唔緊要，都可以傾下<br />\n<br />\n數學有好多嘢係唔理應用層面而推出，由定義開始，用邏輯擴展開去，足以證明數學嘅獨立性<br />\n例子係未有密碼學前嘅number theory<br />\n<br />\nPhysics嗰邊，喺我認識範圍入面嘅都會連到一堆數學同統計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"物理無咗數學會冇咁完整姐<br />\n唔會無說服力既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係observe到個現象然後用model解釋番個現象,數學係用係個model到,但係observe到個現象可以完全唔關數學事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁個現象真係發生過,唔會因為我用唔到數學解釋就冇說服力<br />\n例子:<br />\n蘋果跌落黎證明萬有引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算無數學既式去形容萬有引力都好,萬有引力始終存在"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"但如果無數學 physics發現嘅野都只係靠觀察所得 好難再去運用,證實或者更進一步推論 <br />\n咁嘅話同神秘學啲鳩up有乜分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec144f35b7a2d920ddcb0f54e83e88a85aa9760","tid":1096202,"uid":87339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7592b796b23841845473deb1d2843e532d5344d6","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"數學係可以好獨立咁發展<br />\nPhysics無咗數學同統計就無說服力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"物理始終係實驗結果為重<br />\n<br />\n萬有引力係吸力冇數學同統計啦掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇說服力？"},{"pid":"97f416c3b644c539235c1aa0c61b8a0be0cf1b82","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cd30650acfd8f3cb5120bf50056b4e3a1fd1852","tid":1096202,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"50c71e10f7c852b3b716e3d2e273d819fd0a8cf6","tid":1096202,"uid":86196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bc43938080630499a27de3682d4ed02f61e1cf3f","tid":1096202,"uid":838,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"都預咗會有負皮<br />\n討論區都係講自己睇法㗎啦，唔support唔緊要，都可以傾下<br />\n<br />\n數學有好多嘢係唔理應用層面而推出，由定義開始，用邏輯擴展開去，足以證明數學嘅獨立性<br />\n例子係未有密碼學前嘅number theory<br />\n<br />\nPhysics嗰邊，喺我認識範圍入面嘅都會連到一堆數學同統計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"物理無咗數學會冇咁完整姐<br />\n唔會無說服力既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係observe到個現象然後用model解釋番個現象,數學係用係個model到,但係observe到個現象可以完全唔關數學事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁個現象真係發生過,唔會因為我用唔到數學解釋就冇說服力<br />\n例子:<br />\n蘋果跌落黎證明萬有引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算無數學既式去形容萬有引力都好,萬有引力始終存在"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"但如果無數學 physics發現嘅野都只係靠觀察所得 好難再去運用,證實或者更進一步推論 <br />\n咁嘅話同神秘學啲鳩up有乜分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:02:05.000Z","msg":"靠觀察所得係建基於事實,係可被推翻/可被驗證<br />\n而神秘學係靠個fd個fd個fd(sample size=1，而其實有冇哩個fd都唔知)所講就話係，最重要係神秘學唔可以用實驗證明，或者已經可以被科學推翻，而physics就可以不停靠做實驗論證<br />\n由幾時開始你覺得加咗數學就唔可以係鳩up?"}]}